      },
      {
        "id": "insc-2",
        "text": "12.01.05 - 12.03.23",
        "font": {
          "family": "Adorable",
          "size_px": 14
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 72,
          "y_px": -300
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-3",
        "text": "That your presence on this earth is felt by all.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 158.965,
          "y_px": -248
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-4",
        "text": "And the admiration for you is not small.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 167.457,
          "y_px": -220
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-5",
        "text": "Not by the things you say and do,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 167.455,
          "y_px": -196.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-6",
        "text": "But by everything that makes you, you.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 157.46,
          "y_px": -172.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-7",
        "text": "What words can be spoken to mend my heart?",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 141.969,
          "y_px": -151
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-8",
        "text": "Now that we are forever apart.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 170.946,
          "y_px": -128.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-9",
        "text": "There are no words that can stop these tears,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 166.454,
          "y_px": -108
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-10",
        "text": "Like watching the sun as it disappears.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 173.952,
          "y_px": -84.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-11",
        "text": "Words can be spoken, written and sung,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 172.452,
          "y_px": -63
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-12",
        "text": "And you will always be forever young.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 182.451,
          "y_px": -38.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-13",
        "text": "May it be known that you are in our hearts,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -197.996,
          "y_px": -11.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-14",
        "text": "While we watch the ship as it departs.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -221.998,
          "y_px": 13
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-15",
        "text": "You are now dancing with angels above.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -211.497,
          "y_px": 34
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-16",
        "text": "Peaceful and free with so much love.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -222.998,
          "y_px": 57
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-17",
        "text": "I do not wish to say the word goodbye,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -213,
          "y_px": 79
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-18",
        "text": "For I will miss you too much I will not lie.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -201,
          "y_px": 104
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-19",
        "text": "There are no words that one can say,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -223.501,
          "y_px": 127.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-20",
        "text": "To ease the pain and make it go away.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -222,
          "y_px": 149.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-21",
        "text": "Instead you will live forever in my heart and mind.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -162,
          "y_px": 170
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-22",
        "text": "Go forth and shine and leave us behind.",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -211,
          "y_px": 195
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-23",
        "text": "I will search for you in rainbows and stars,",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -199,
          "y_px": 220
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-24",
        "text": "You will be the brightest one by far.\"",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": -228,
          "y_px": 242
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
        "surface": "headstone/front"
      },
      {
        "id": "insc-25",
        "text": "\"How much do you really mean to  me?",
        "font": {
          "family": "Garamond",
          "size_px": 9
        },
        "position": {
          "x_px": 157.465,
          "y_px": -266.5
        },
        "rotation": {
          "z_deg": 0
        },
        "color": "#ffffff",
